Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光\N龙咲海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风以她关怀同伴的心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏了幻惑士卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要她们自相残杀的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜被\N光、海、风的心打动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应和阿斯克特一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这场战斗抽身后离去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光、海、风 无法割舍的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只魔物先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是它的本体!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是皮外伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你真仁慈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然来到锡菲罗后已过了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当我们受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还担心得要哭似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担心我们 我们好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也要保重自己的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…我不想再有人死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有时会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我快点强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅或许就不用死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一定要成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 虽然小风你拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断对普蕾西雅\N用愈之风…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的回复魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能令死去的人复活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是什么也做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初我不相信这里是异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是听从别人的吩咐前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被古列夫吩咐成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想能够的话就做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是因为憧憬或兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非经过深思熟虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现曾在锡菲罗帮助我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫、普蕾西雅和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 幸好有小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小光一起真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是战斗完了就走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后竟然又要由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软绵绵的莫歌拿带路继续旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路途遥远 我们要加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 为了成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要经历多久的旅程才行?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…地图吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那点光是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动…动了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾蒂露娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默之森…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[这]…这张地图?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是这点光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默之森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾蒂路娜之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红、蓝、绿表示我们三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这条线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们一直以来经过的路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在海之神殿入口的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是有魔神的神殿所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我们已经走了这么长的路程了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在 我们在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用地图表示起来 好像电视游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会成长的武器和护甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是RPG世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出公主殿下拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以故事来说也好吻合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是现实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然能用地图表示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始你为何不使用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是吝啬而不拿出来吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RPG是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 电视游戏…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没玩过 完全没玩过?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 有兄弟吗?  有三个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人玩电视游戏吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家是剑道道场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会练剑 一起打扫道场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光的男生口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是受哥哥的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你练剑道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在学校加入了箭道部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看小风射箭的英姿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久之后有场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要来哦 可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N一定!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也邀请你来我的剑击比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能尽快回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们加油吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊?小风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我想趁\N大家雄心壮志时出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要用愈之风治好伤势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿 起程了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿 不可跑得太远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些光是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那些光是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海和小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被那些光吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道小海和小风怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海和小风…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们被捉走了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我猜她们被捉走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一回头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像光墙一样的东西突然经过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小海和小风吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光墙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫 你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我未听过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是古列夫\N也不知道的魔物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现今锡菲罗出没的魔物中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一小部份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗的魔物是窥伺特殊情形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由人们的不安形成的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由不安形成的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主用她意志的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撑着这个世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她祈求锡菲罗永远和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为人们安居乐业的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令锡菲罗维持为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个没有异常气象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平和美丽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 艾美诺公主现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能祈求锡菲罗安定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 风云变色 地动山摇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些天变地异
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上知道神官谢加图叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们被恐惧和不安笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的心创造出新的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那些魔物…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是心实体化后的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…\N不安或恐惧的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生出那些魔物吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉去海和风的魔物我也不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得通讯的时间缩短了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫也在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找寻小海和小风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常快的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先要想出追上它的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海她们现在究竟在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要知道地点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊!莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张地图!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张地图!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿你让我们看的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就知道和小风在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在移动的这点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这点光在哪个方向吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你真仁慈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担心我们 我们好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也要保重自己的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光你练剑道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在学校加入了箭道部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也邀请你来我的剑击比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能尽快回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们加油吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!等我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…\N我一定会去救你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好像有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要救小风她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人一起回去东京!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己下了那决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小海小风许下承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违背诺言…\N我绝对做不到!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人一起…\N成为魔法骑士!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些光…\N为何攻击小海和小风?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它攻击移动的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我也在移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才…\N莫歌拿救我时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和当时的两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才的共通点是…\N什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是血!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时…\N小海和小风…在流血!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而刚才的我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…被血吸引…\N而出现!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由心生出来的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何伤得那么重!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事!?\N又有魔物吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人战斗太勉强了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有小海和小风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在我身边努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士拯救锡菲罗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 一起回去东京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈之风!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起程吧 去唤醒下一部魔神!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:46.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:59.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:11.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:24.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
